                    "stepText": "Now, using the result of $!$T^4$!$, calculate the product $!$\\sigma T^4$!$. Here, $!$\\sigma$!$ is the Stefan\u2013Boltzmann constant, $5.67\\times10^{-8} \\frac{W}{m^2 K^4}$. What is $!$\\sigma T^4$!$? (Remember that the units will be in $!$W/m^2$!$.)",
